    <field name="scopecontent_teim">This series documents Berkowitz's family, particularly his father, Milton Berkowitz.  The series contains a small amount of correspondence between Richard Berkowitz and various family members and between other members of the family; home movies from the 1950s; and photographs of Berkowitz, his parents, his brothers, and their families.  Materials related to Milton Berkowitz include his scrapbook created during his tour of duty in the United Kingdom and Germany with the United States Army in World War II; his collection of stag films; and his dues books from the Bricklayers, Masons and Plasterers' International Union of America.</field>
